XIII 06 - The Jason Fly Case
With the conspiracy that nearly claimed his life dismantled, XIII can finally turn all his attention towards uncovering his own distant past. Armed with everything he could find on Jason Fly - the man he seems to be - he heads to Green Falls, where he grew up. The problem with amnesia is that you never know exactly what youÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ll dig up when you go home again. And... is everything really solved concerning the presidential assassination that cost him his memory?
