XIII 08 - Thirteen to One
XIII survived the trip back to his childhood home. The Mongoose has finally been caught and is in a high-security jail. But there is still one piece of the puzzle missing, and when President Sheridan asks him to discover who the Number I is, the man now known as Jason McLane doesnÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t hesitate for long. His best chance: finding Kim Rowland wherever she may be hiding. But the Mongoose has powerful allies and wonÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t stay locked up forever...
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://i.imgbox.com/adfqZbkP.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
