XIII 011 - Three Silver Watches
XIII has freed a country, exposed a traitor, reunited with his wife... and found his father. As he deals - somewhat against his will - with the aftermath of the revolution in Costa Verde, Sean Mullway recounts for him his familyÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s history: Irish immigrants, remorseless Mafiosi, Mexican gold, and three silver watches. New answers will also bring new questions and a whole new set of potential enemies just as old ones come back to the fore.
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://i.imgbox.com/acrLKtQX.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
