XIII 013 - Top Secret
The Mongoose is dead. So is Number I. But, since he was the President of the United States, XIIIÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s friends are all on the run again. McLane, though, has been arrested, and heÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s being judged in secret by the heads of the American intelligence community. Sentenced to life in a secret prison, he has no illusions that heÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ll ever reach it. The ruthlessness of the NSA Director proves him right - but heÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s not the only one who wants XIII dead.
