http://i.imgbox.com/abeb2V5m.jpg&lt;/a&gt;


XIII 014 - Release the Hounds!
Having escaped from the clutches of IrinaÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s organisation, XIII is on the loose in America but still hunted by both GiordinoÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s NSA and IrinaÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s top assassin, Jessica. As he tries to return to his friends in San Miguel, heÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s forced to dodge bullets and outsmart various traps and ambushes. With the odds stacked against him, he will have to rely on help from an enemy and his own mounting anger at the constant string of attacks.
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://i.imgbox.com/acb5s3dQ.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
