http://i.imgbox.com/adymaJfg.jpg&lt;/a&gt;


XIII 015 - Operation Montecristo
Arrested by the Costaverdean authorities because of pressure from the US, XIII and his friends are awaiting their extradition. Instead, theyÃ¢â‚¬â„¢re freed by Costaverdean troops in disguise. But they canÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t afford to stick around, as theyÃ¢â‚¬â„¢re still on the run from the most powerful nation on Earth. Desperate for money, McLane decides to go after MaximilianÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s gold, as Mullway believes heÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s found the location of the third silver watch. The problem is that the location is under 150 feet of water...
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://i.imgbox.com/acf9hwm4.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
