XIII 018 - The Last Round
XIII and his friends have failed to recover MaximilianÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s gold and are tired of hiding, running and struggling. When two books come out in the USA relating all the events of the amnesiacÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s life and the details of the Conspiracy of the XX, they see it as a possible chance to come out in the open and trust in their countryÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s justice. But they still have enemies, at home and abroad, and everyone is set on a collision course...
